data.description: Welcome to your dream home in South Daytona! This charming 3-bedroom block home is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.  As you enter there is a large living room and separate dining area. The windows throughout the home, replaced in 2019, flood the interior with natural light.  The kitchen boasts modern appliances and flows into the spacious family room.  Enjoy the expansive backyard, complete with a shed for additional storage and the screened-in porch.  Practical updates include 2019 AC, and water heater. Located in close proximity to the Daytona Speedway and Daytona Beach, you'll have easy access to entertainment, dining, and recreational activities.   All this with no HOA!   A buyer's premium of $10,000 is due at closing
